wonderful mother in the world.

1:20:21.822 --> 1:20:24.691
Go away. I want
you to disappear.

1:20:24.693 --> 1:20:29.228
After you killed her, you drove
to one of your construction sites.

1:20:29.230 --> 1:20:31.934
You took Isabelle's
body with you.

1:21:27.188 --> 1:21:31.490
<i>You had committed
the perfect crime.</i>

1:21:31.492 --> 1:21:34.160
<i>No one ever found the body,</i>

1:21:34.162 --> 1:21:39.802
and the airport is a tomb
that can't be penetrated.

1:21:51.345 --> 1:21:55.748
I didn't kill Isabelle.
I was madly in love with her.

1:21:55.750 --> 1:21:58.151
Who is talking when you talk?

1:21:58.153 --> 1:21:59.788
You.

1:22:16.604 --> 1:22:17.772
Do it fast.

1:23:46.527 --> 1:23:48.564
<i>I love you, Jeremy.</i>

1:24:38.750 --> 1:24:40.708
You didn't kill your wife.

1:24:40.792 --> 1:24:42.667
You didn't kill your wife.

1:24:42.833 --> 1:24:44.750
She left you.

1:24:45.375 --> 1:24:47.708
She is still alive.

1:25:19.086 --> 1:25:21.954
<i>Like Antoine
de Saint-Exupéry said,</i>

1:25:21.956 --> 1:25:26.359
<i>"Perfection is achieved not when
there is nothing more to add.</i>

1:25:26.361 --> 1:25:30.866
<i>But when there is nothing
left to take away."</i>
